data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCsePersonCsePersonCaseServiceProvider
data.value: select distinct T5.CSP_NUMBER, T7.CSP_NUMBER, T3.NUMB, T3.STATUS, T3.STATUS_DATE, T3.CSE_OPEN_DATE, T3.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T3.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, T3.NO_JURISDICTION_CD, T4.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T4.USER_ID, T4.ROLE_CODE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T4, CKT_CASE T3 join CKT_CASE_ROLE T5 on T5.TYPE = 'AP' and T5.END_DATE >= @endDate and T5.START_DATE <= @startDate and T3.NUMB = T5.CAS_NUMBER join CKT_CASE_ROLE T7 on T7.TYPE = 'CH' and T7.END_DATE >= @endDate and T7.START_DATE <= @startDate and T3.NUMB = T7.CAS_NUMBER where exists ( select * from CKT_LEG_ACT_CAS_RL T6 where T5.CASE_ROLE_ID = T6.CRO_IDENTIFIER and T5.TYPE = T6.CRO_TYPE and T5.CSP_NUMBER = T6.CSP_NUMBER and T5.CAS_NUMBER = T6.CAS_NUMBER and @lgaId = T6.LGA_ID ) and exists ( select * from CKT_LEG_ACT_CAS_RL T8 where T7.CASE_ROLE_ID = T8.CRO_IDENTIFIER and T7.TYPE = T8.CRO_TYPE and T7.CSP_NUMBER = T8.CSP_NUMBER and T7.CAS_NUMBER = T8.CAS_NUMBER and @lgaId = T8.LGA_ID ) and exists ( select * from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T9 where T3.NUMB = T9.CAS_NO and T9.REASON_CODE = 'RSP' and T9.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @startDate and T9.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @startDate and T4.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T9.SPD_ID ) order by T3.NUMB desc, T4.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID desc

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, NEW_ORD_EST from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and (REPORT_LEVEL in ('AT', 'CA', 'CW'))

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, NEW_ORD_EST from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadLegalActionAssigmentServiceProvider
data.value: select T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.OSP_ROLE_CODE, T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.END_DT, T1.REASON_CODE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T2.USER_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 join CKT_LA_SERV_PROV T1 on @lgaIdentifier = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER and T1.EFFECTIVE_DT <= @effectiveDt and T1.END_DT >= @endDt and T1.OSP_ROLE_CODE is not null and T1.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE is not null and T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID is not null and T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID order by T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID

data.name: ReadLegalActionFipsTribunalLegalAction
data.value: select * from ( select LEGAL_ACTION_ID, CLASSIFICATION, ACTION_TAKEN, TYPE, FILED_DT, COURT_CASE_NO, END_DT, STANDARD_NO, CREATED_TSTAMP, ESTABLISHMENT_CD, TRB_ID from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION where (FILED_DT between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and STANDARD_NO > @standardNo and (ESTABLISHMENT_CD in ('CS', 'CT')) and CLASSIFICATION = 'J' and ( ACTION_TAKEN in ('DEFJPATJ', 'DFLTSUPJ', 'JEF', 'MEDEXPJ', 'PATERNJ', 'PATMEDJ', 'PATONLYJ', 'SUPPORTJ', 'VOLPATTJ', 'VOLSUPTJ', 'VOL718BJ', '718BDEFJ', '718BJERJ') ) ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) T1.[STATE], T1.COUNTY, T1.LOCATION, T1.COUNTY_DESC, T1.STATE_ABBREVIATION, T2.TRIBUNAL_NM, T2.JUDICIAL_DISTRICT, T2.IDENTIFIER from CKT_FIPS T1 join CKT_TRIBUNAL T2 on T2.IDENTIFIER = S1.TRB_ID and T1.LOCATION = T2.FIP_LOCATION and T1.COUNTY = T2.FIP_COUNTY and T1.[STATE] = T2.FIP_STATE and T1.COUNTY > 0 ) S2 outer apply ( select top(1) LEGAL_ACTION_ID, CLASSIFICATION, ACTION_TAKEN, TYPE, FILED_DT, STANDARD_NO, CREATED_TSTAMP, ESTABLISHMENT_CD from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION where STANDARD_NO = S1.STANDARD_NO and FILED_DT < @date1 and (ESTABLISHMENT_CD in ('CS', 'CT')) and CLASSIFICATION = 'J' and ( ACTION_TAKEN in ('DEFJPATJ', 'DFLTSUPJ', 'JEF', 'MEDEXPJ', 'PATERNJ', 'PATMEDJ', 'PATONLYJ', 'SUPPORTJ', 'VOLPATTJ', 'VOLSUPTJ', 'VOL718BJ', '718BDEFJ', '718BJERJ') ) ) S3 order by S1.STANDARD_NO, S1.FILED_DT

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set NEW_ORD_EST = @newOrdEst where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, NEW_ORD_EST = @newOrdEst where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
